<strong><a class="contextual" name="4"></a>Viewing and Updating Your Information on Meeting Tomorrow</strong>

You are responsible for updating and maintaining the truth and accuracy of the information you provide to us via this Site. If you want to update Information that you have provided to us via this Site, you may do so by visiting the "My Account" section of this Site.

While we will make reasonable efforts to comply with your request to modify information, you should be aware that it is not always possible to completely delete or modify all information in our databases and servers. Additionally, we may intentionally retain information you have requested us to modify or delete in certain circumstances, such as to resolve disputes, troubleshoot problems and enforce our agreements with you. Further, we are unable to modify information in the records of any third party who has been provided with this information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

